title: 3 Bed/2 Bath Rambler South Everett
posting_body: ['house will be ready for move in 10/1/22.', 'old pictures taken awhile back and will be updated soon.', 'one year lease required and proof of current employment required.', 'must pass criminal background checks about $30 fee non refundable online screening.', 'Serious inquiries only please', 'please dont waste time request touring until info about yourself provided as requested below:', '1.', 'how many adults and children in your family and relationship?', '2.', 'how many adults currently employed and what kind of work they do and how long at current jobs?', '3.', 'what is the income amount of each person?', '4.', 'can you afford first/last/deposit upfront.', '5.', 'any pets if so, what are they and how big?', '6.', 'what is your earliest move in date?', '7. tell me a bit about your financial credit history.', '8. must pass eviction and criminal background screening.', '1500 sft rambler with 100ft x 100ft lot', '3 bedrooms with a master bath', '2 full baths included a master bedroom', 'a big bonus room which can be used for dining area.', 'front and backyard all fenced with big barn style shed for storage', 'sliding door accessible to back deck and fenced backyard', 'big shed at the backyard corner', '20 mins walk to MARINER high school and VOYAGER middle school.', 'floor tile (kitchen, laundry room, bathrooms).', 'laminate flooring throughout the house', 'electric forced air furnace', 'plenty of parking space on asphalt pavement', '10,000sft lot has backyard all fenced and trees along the fence for privacy.', 'greenbelt facing backyard.', 'house sits far from neighbors', 'Close to Alderwood mall and I-5/405/hwy 99', 'first/ last and $2,500 deposit required.', 'thank you for looking', 'Tri Le']
